sellerCard.oneLiner: Professional Web Developer Wordpress Security Pro and Web Designer
sellerCard.description:
Hello, I'm Dumitru B, a professional web developer with experience since 2007 in web development, SEO, and security solutions for CMS-based websites such as WordPress, Joomla. etc. With a strong track record of building over 600 websites and successfully removing malware from more than 3,000 websites in the past two years alone, I am confident in delivering high-quality results. I have been working with websites since the Dial-Up era, combining old-school expertise with up-to-date skills.

If you have any project needs, please feel free to reach out to me, and I will respond promptly.

description.content:
Elevate Your Online Presence with a Stunning Website!

Are you launching a new business?

Or perhaps you're thinking of giving your current website a fresh, modern makeover?


Look no further!


Why choose me?

  • Tailored to Your Brand: Crafting websites that resonate with your brand's colors and style.
  • Flexibility in Design: Whether you prefer theme-based designs or a fully custom look, I got you covered.
  • User-Friendly CMS: Update your content anytime with platforms like WordPress (DIVI, Elementor Pro, Astra Pro, Generate Press) and Joomla (Joomshaper).
  • Decades of Expertise: With over 16 years in web design and development, I'm bringing a wealth of experience to the table.
  • SEO-Ready: My websites are structured for optimal search engine visibility.
  • Post-Launch Support: I'm here for you, even after your website goes live.


Key Features Include (but not limited to):

  • Mobile-Responsive Design
  • Intuitive Admin Panel
  • Integrated Live Chat
  • Google Maps & Analytics
  • Contact Forms
  • Social Media Links
  • Engaging Call-to-Action Widgets
  • Client Testimonials
  • E-Commerce Capabilities


Not Sure Which Package Suits You?

Predefined packages are designed to guide you. However, if they don't align, Message ME.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
First and most important, I will need to know as much as possible about you and your business, that way I'll be able to make you a site that truly represents you.
Other than that, I will need access to your hosting account / existing website.
A reference or an example page would help a lot.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you Redesign my site ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes i can redesign your website using your existing contents

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you SEO my Website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes i also provide SEO services ( In page SEO  services )
pm me for a quote.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you make my site mobile friendly / Responsive
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes. This can be done! just send me the link and i will let you know the price.
In most cases a rebuild might be needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a “unique page"?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A unique page is a page in your website that has a unique(not template) design. Unique pages are Homepage, About, Contact, Services etc. a Non-unique page is a page that is generated automatically from the site, for example, the product pages in an online store, or the article pages in a blog.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to easily modify the contents of the site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! Once the website is done, you will be able to not only change the texts and images with a few clicks, but also to change the layout or add new pages. If you can change your facebook image you will be able to change an image

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is White Label? - White Labeling and how it works.
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
The terms white label and private label can be used interchangeably. White labeling is when a product or service removes their brand and logo from the end product :
for exemple " © All rights reserved to Your Company  Ltd  / Developed by Dumitru

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you upgrade my 1.5 / 2.5 Joomla to latest version
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, this can be done, I would call it a Rebuild rather than an upgrade since there is no simple and easy way to upgrade from this  old version and it's better to create from the ground new site using your content.
this will give you a stable site

questionsAndAnswers.question: Creation Process - an overview
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
1-  Choose a theme or send the custom design 
2-  Add needed plugins 
3-  Add in original content (must be provided)
4-  Customize website to your needs
